<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mitzu Crew - Roblox Dah Hood</title>
    <style>
        /* CSS styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin: 20px;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        nav ul li {
            display: inline;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        nav ul li a:hover {
            background-color: #555;
        }

        main {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        #hero {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 50px 20px;
            margin: 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        #hero h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            color: #333;
        }

        #hero p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        #hero button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        #hero button:hover {
            background-color: #555;
        }

        #hero img {
            max-width: 200px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

        #features {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin: 20px;
        }

        .feature {
            flex: 1 1 calc(33.33% - 20px);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .feature h3 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .feature p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .feature ol {
            text-align: left;
        }

        .feature img {
            max-width: 200px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            float: right;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

        .feature a {
            color: #333;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .feature a:hover {
            background-color: #555;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: calc(100% - 40px);
            margin: 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Mitzu Crew</h1>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Members</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>
    
    <main>
        <section id="hero">
            <div>
                <h1>Welcome to Mitzu Crew!</h1>
                <p>Your ultimate Roblox Dah Hood crew. Join our community and be a part of something epic!</p>
                <button onclick="window.location.href='https://discord.gg/BfAE399j3Z'">Join Discord</button>
            </div>
            <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Mitzu Crew">
        </section>
        
        <section id="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>About Us</h3>
                <p>Mitzu Crew is led by Mitsuzukii, and we run the streets of Dah Hood. Join us and become a part of our 180+ loyal members!</p>
                <a href="https://www.roblox.com/groups/13005432/Mitzu-Crew#!/about">Join Our Roblox Group</a>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Steps to Join Our Crew</h3>
                <p>Follow these steps to join our crew in-game:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>First, join our group by clicking the button below.</li>
                    <li>After you have joined, copy the group ID: <strong>13005432</strong>.</li>
                    <li>In the game, click the three-man icon next to settings.</li>
                    <li>Paste the group ID and you are done! Welcome to the crew!</li>
                </ol>
                <a href="https://www.roblox.com/groups/13005432/Mitzu-Crew#!/about">Join Our Roblox Group</a>
                <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="How to join our crew">
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Contact</h3>
                <p>Have any questions or want to get in touch with us? Join our Discord server and chat with the team directly.</p>
                <a href="https://discord.gg/BfAE399j3Z">Contact Us</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    
    

    <script>
        // JavaScript for dynamic elements can be added here if needed
    </script>
</body>
</html>
